        thermostats) through the web. And, on top of it, we have all the experience to create
        the best mobile experience based on your needs.
        </p>
        <p><a class="button-add" href="mailto:touch@lelylan.com">Contact us &rarr;</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <hr/>
    </div>

    <div class="inner row">
      <div class="right small">
        <%= image_tag 'makers/kickstarter.png' %>
