        the hardware, we help you on the software.
        </p>

        <p>
        <a class="button-add" href="mailto:touch@lelylan.com">Contact us &rarr;</a>
        <a class="button-add" href="http://ezcontrol.it">Checkout the EZControl Indiegogo campaign &rarr;</a>
        </p>

      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <hr/>
    </div>

    <div class="inner row">
      <div class="left big">
        <h2>Lelylan Private Cloud</h2>
        <p>
        Do you want your own Lelylan? We offer you Lelylan Private Cloud, your own instance
        of Lelylan for your own products. It runs on your local servers or on any cloud
        infrastructure, such as Amazon Web Services or Google Cloud Platform.
        </p>
        <p>
        <a class="button-add" href="mailto:touch@lelylan.com">Contact us &rarr;</a>
        <span class="button-add button-disabled">Lelylan Private Cloud coming 1Q 2015</span>
