        And if you need help, we'll be happy to tailor the best User Experience for your products.
        </p>
        <p>
        <a class="button-add" href="mailto:touch@lelylan.com">Contact us &rarr;</a>
        <a class="button-add" href="http://github.com/lelylan/devices-dashboard-ng/">Get source code on Github &rarr;</a>
